title: ETH v1 Update: Raise $CEL collateral factor
body:
Intro: This is a vote to raise the collateral factor of CEL on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market, with collateral cap.

 Proposal: https://forum.cream.finance/t/cel-token-collateral-factor-change-0-to-25-on-ethereum/1995

 Rational: CEL is liquid on dex’s. CREAM will be the first to CEL as collateral in defi.

For:
Raise collateral factor of $CEL to 45% with a collateral cap of $1.25M (210437 cel tokens).

Against:
Do not make any changes to CEL market on ETH v1.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
